WEBVTT

00:02.792 --> 00:04.139
I'm asking you to marry me.

00:04.143 --> 00:06.574
We might as well
just go to Vegas and elope.

00:06.580 --> 00:09.854
If we're gonna have a family we'll need
to turn the second bedroom into a nursery.

00:09.864 --> 00:11.736
But.. that's where Jake stays.

00:11.737 --> 00:14.969
Yeah, but once Alan moves out, then Jake
won't be staying here anymore, right?

00:14.976 --> 00:17.444
- Alan is moving out?
- Of course he is...

00:18.643 --> 00:19.484
Isn't he?

00:19.485 --> 00:21.475
I said the wedding's off.

00:21.478 --> 00:23.292
Can I borrow your wedding ring?

00:23.293 --> 00:24.197
What for?

00:24.209 --> 00:26.364
I thought as long we are in Vegas...

00:26.365 --> 00:28.049
I'd marry Kandy.

00:28.756 --> 00:31.503
And I now pronounce you man and wife,
you may kiss the bride.

00:31.522 --> 00:33.744
I don't freaking believe it!

00:33.745 --> 00:36.808
Cheer up Charlie, you're finally
getting what you always wanted,

00:36.812 --> 00:38.343
I'm moving out of your house!

00:38.355 --> 00:41.100
I don't freaking believe it!

00:44.255 --> 00:46.512
Do we have time to play
roulette before we go?

00:46.512 --> 00:49.919
Oh honey, that is a sucker's game,
the odds are totally stacked against you

00:49.934 --> 00:53.195
Ooooh...Super Slots'o'Fun Jackpot!

00:54.764 --> 00:57.338
Sure... Make the smart bet.

00:58.301 --> 01:00.549
Here honey, kiss it
before I put it in.

01:00.561 --> 01:02.770
And the honeymoon begins...

01:03.831 --> 01:07.274
Slots'o'Fun, get it?
It's lots of fun!

01:08.579 --> 01:11.084
I'm ready for a refill.

01:16.202 --> 01:18.026
Is that good?

01:20.779 --> 01:22.335
I won...

01:23.689 --> 01:26.368
I won a half a million dollars!

01:28.754 --> 01:31.267
I don't freaking believe it...

01:31.865 --> 01:33.251
Alan, you're rich!

01:33.257 --> 01:36.966
No we're rich!
We're married now, what's mine is yours!

01:37.305 --> 01:38.834
Really?

01:39.335 --> 01:41.647
And the honeymoon ends...

